=== TEST 2: set content-length of response headers
--- config
location = /ngx_header {
	content_by_php '
		$str = "Testing ngx_header!\n";
		echo $str;
		ngx_header_set("Content-Length", strlen($str));
	';
}
--- request
GET /ngx_header
--- response_headers
Content-Length: 20
--- response_body
Testing ngx_header!



